DOCNAME: CASE OF ANDREY MEDVEDEV v. RUSSIA
CONCLUSION: Pecuniary damage - award (Article 41 - Pecuniary damage;Just satisfaction)
JUDGES: Alena Poláčková;Branko Lubarda;Dmitry Dedov;Helen Keller;Helena Jäderblom;Luis López Guerra;Pere Pastor Vilanova
TEXT: CARDINAL . Following the delivery of the judgment by ORG in the applicant ’s case , the applicant lodged an application with ORG of GPE , asking it to review the judgment of DATE as upheld on DATE by the ORG whereby ORG had revoked the applicant ’s title to the flat located at MONEY , GPE , ordered his eviction and returned the flat to GPE .
CARDINAL . On DATE ORG dismissed the applicant ’s application . The applicant appealed . The parties have not informed ORG outcome of the proceedings .
